description: Fasadgruppen Group AB engages in the installation and renovation of building facades. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 1,004 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-12-09. The firm provides services related to facades, masonry, cleaning, windows and balconies, roofs, scaffolding and carbon fiber reinforcement. The main consumers of the group are property owners, construction companies, property managers, consultants, tenant-owner associations, the state, municipalities and county councils. Fasadgruppen Group operates in the Nordic region.
name: Fasadgruppen Group AB (publ)
